snippet.title: Goeland - Gameplay Preview
snippet.description:
Play as a seagull in a sandbox-style open world where you can help, bother, or manipulate the inhabitants in a cheerful atmosphere.
In this non-linear experience, you are free to do as you please, in any order you choose.
Let your wings decide the fate of this charming adventure in this highly interactive and humor-filled experience!

Be a part of the journey by adding Goeland to your wishlist today!


PLAY THE DEMO ON STEAM: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2531840/Goeland?utm_source=youtube&utm_campaign=trailer
